                                                    <div class="card-body faqs-answer" style="padding-left: 25px;">
                                                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Because a 1BHK has limited
                                                                space, you can use interior design hacks to arrange your
                                                                1BHK flat. Here are some ways in which you can define
                                                                and arrange your 1BHK flat:</span></p>
                                                        <ol>
                                                            <li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span
                                                                    style="font-weight: 400;">Use colour as a tool to
                                                                    make your space look bigger. Go for lighter colours
                                                                    — a classic white and cream combination can make a
                                                                    1BHK look spacious and airy </span></li>
                                                            <li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span
                                                                    style="font-weight: 400;">Invest in modular <a
                                                                        href="<?php echo base_url(''); ?>">multifunctional
                                                                        furniture</a> that multiples the storage option
                                                                    in your 1BHK. For example, use a multipurpose TV
                                                                    unit with storage, use divan beds, buy wardrobes
                                                                    with loft storage and multiple drawers.</span></li>
                                                            <li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span
                                                                    style="font-weight: 400;">Go for all things minimal
